{
  "stem": "20083.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 15.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And-- and he was visiting a cousin or a niece on the same floor.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And I remember when the elevator started to move again and the doors opened, there were the nurses and the doctors outside the elevator giving the Hitler salute.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And Hitler-- Goring pushed me right in front of him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And of course, it was a very strange experience, as you can imagine, being greeted with, by about 20 people giving the Hitler salute.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I did not.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Neither did Goring.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was not in a uniform, he was in a very light, white raincoat.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But that was my experience with Goring.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then after he had visited his cousin, I had-- the door to my father's room was always open.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "After he had visited his cousin, he came back through the hallway and he looked, probably-- he looked into the room where my father was together with me.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he saw me or recognized me and he came in and shock my father's hand.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Now my father for some reason had the-- won the Iron Cross in the First World War and had the Iron Cross for some reason, I cannot remember why, on his night table.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And Goring saw it and picked it up, and it was the Iron Cross First Class.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he patted my father on the shoulder, not realizing that he was Jewish, and wished him all the best.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And my father was absolutely in a state of shock.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, he did recognize him, of course.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You cannot help but with all the SS bodyguards behind them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So but that was my experience with Goring.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I have no idea.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You have to realize at that time in 1937, I was about 14 years old.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I really did not ask these questions.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
